---
title: "create-sequences — Draft and write a sequence diagram into the target project"
---
%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude
    participant FS as File System

    User->>Claude: /create-sequences <name> [description]

    note over Claude,FS: Preflight
    Claude->>Claude: START_TS = date +%s<br/>DISPLAY_TS = date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S
    Claude->>FS: Check .claude/sequences/ exists in cwd
    FS-->>Claude: present / absent
    alt .claude/ absent
        Claude->>User: .claude/ not found.<br/>Run /init-project first.
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end

    note over Claude,User: Phase: Detect participants
    Claude->>Claude: Parse <description> for entity hints +<br/>apply rules/mermaid-style.md naming
    Claude->>User: Candidate participants:<br/>- User (actor)<br/>- Browser<br/>- API<br/>- DB<br/>Confirm / add / remove?
    User-->>Claude: Final participant list

    note over Claude,User: Phase: Sketch flow
    Claude->>Claude: Draft 5-15 message-list<br/>(sender -> receiver: action)
    Claude->>User: Sketch preview:<br/>1. User -> Browser: ...<br/>2. Browser -> API: ...<br/>...<br/>Approve / edit / reorder?
    User-->>Claude: Approved sketch

    note over Claude,User: Phase: Draft diagram
    Claude->>Claude: Expand sketch into full .mmd<br/>following:<br/>- rules/mermaid-style.md<br/>- docs/how-to-create-mermaid.md<br/>- rules/no-step-numbers.md
    Claude->>User: Full .mmd preview<br/>(in a box, for review)
    User-->>Claude: Write as-is / iterate once

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Write
    opt File already exists at target path
        Claude->>FS: Read existing .mmd
        FS-->>Claude: current content
        Claude->>User: File exists — show diff<br/>[o]verwrite / [m]erge / [c]ancel
        User-->>Claude: choice
    end
    Claude->>FS: Write <project-root>/.claude/sequences/<slug>.mmd
    FS-->>Claude: OK

    note over Claude,User: Phase: Compact report
    Claude->>Claude: END_TS = date +%s<br/>wall_clock_sec = END_TS - START_TS
    Claude->>User: Compact dashboard:<br/>File, Participants, Messages,<br/>Duration

    Note right of Claude: No separate report file —<br/>single-diagram run doesn't warrant<br/>a .claude/state/reports/ entry.<br/>For bulk multi-diagram runs,<br/>consider /create-docs sequence<br/>or /update-docs --refresh.
